WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.950 --> 00:00:15.530
Hello, my name is Janice, and I work as a nurse at
Eminent Hospice.

2
00:00:25.750 --> 00:00:28.470
I used to work at the nursing home.

3
00:00:29.370 --> 00:00:33.490
It was very rewarding to work with the elderly.

4
00:00:34.550 --> 00:00:39.370
Even if I gave them a little help, it was a big help
to them.

5
00:00:40.530 --> 00:00:47.630
Even if I gave them a word of interest, they were
very smiley and happy.

6
00:00:48.490 --> 00:00:50.850
I felt a lot more rewarding because of that.

7
00:00:51.610 --> 00:00:56.790
One thing I was sad about was that I couldn't have
enough time with them.

8
00:00:56.810 --> 00:01:00.330
One of them asked me to visit the hospice.

9
00:01:00.330 --> 00:01:04.310
At that time, it was only for the patient.

10
00:01:08.410 --> 00:01:15.810
I felt more rewarding because of that.

11
00:01:15.810 --> 00:01:17.850
That's why I started hospice.

12
00:01:26.700 --> 00:01:31.060
When you go to the hospice, you often think of
patients who are not clear-cut.

13
00:01:32.100 --> 00:01:42.200
We help patients with various reasons to prepare for
the end of their lives comfortably.

14
00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:55.560
If I explain in detail, the nurse went to the
hospice and looked at the patient's head from the beginning to the end.

15
00:01:56.260 --> 00:02:01.560
We plan on the problems that are present there and
the problems that can be solved in the future.

16
00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:09.720
After discussing with the doctor, we provide various
treatments for the medicine.

17
